  Create stable candidate.

  25 Mar 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> ruby-shout-2.2.1-r1.ebuild:
  Document ruby22 status.

  16 Oct 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> ruby-shout-2.2.1-r1.ebuild:
  Add ruby21. Update Homepage.

  24 Apr 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> ruby-shout-2.2.1-r1.ebuild,
  ruby-shout-2.2.1.ebuild:
  Remove ruby18 support.

